# Repo-side dev install discipline.
#
# `ignore-scripts=true` blocks lifecycle scripts on `pnpm install` so a
# malicious transitive dep with a `postinstall` hook can't quietly own the
# dev host. Browser binary install is invoked explicitly as a one-shot
# (`pnpm exec playwright-core install chromium`) — never as a lifecycle.
#
# Sibling guideline: see SECURITY.md (D2b).
ignore-scripts=true

